AddToFunc "Move-or-Raise" "M" Raise
+ "M" Move
+ "C" Raise
+						"C" WindowShade 2
+ "D" Maximize 100 100
Mouse 1 W M Move-or-Raise

AddToFunc "Resize-or-Raise" "M" Raise
+ "M" Resize
+ "C" Raise
+ "D" RaiseLower
Mouse 3 W M Resize-or-Raise

OpaqueMoveSize 1000

Style "*" BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1

BorderStyle active Solid black
BorderStyle inactive Solid black
TitleStyle active Solid #056839
TitleStyle inactive Solid #056839

AddToFunc "StartFunction" "I" Module FvwmTaskBar
AddToFunc DeiconifyRaiseAndFocus
+ I Iconify off
+ I Raise
+ I Focus
Style "FvwmTaskBar" NoTitle, !Handles, !Borders, Sticky, WindowListSkip, \
  CirculateSkip, StaysOnBottom, FixedPosition, FixedSize, !Iconifiable
  DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTaskBar: *
*FvwmTaskBar: Geometry +0-0
*FvwmTaskBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTaskBar: Font "xft:Hack:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*FvwmTaskBar: SelFont "xft:Hack:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*FvwmTaskBar: StatusFont "xft:Hack:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*FvwmTaskBar: Fore green #edit this
*FvwmTaskBar: Back black #edit this
*FvwmTaskBar: Colorset 9
*FvwmTaskBar: IconColorset 9
*FvwmTaskBar: FocusColorset 9
*FvwmTaskBar: TipsColorset 9
*FvwmTaskBar: UseSkipList
*FvwmTaskBar: UseIconNames
*FvwmTaskBar: ShowTips
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click1 DeiconifyRaiseAndFocus
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click2 Iconify On
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click3 Lower
*FvwmTaskBar: ButtonWidth 180
*FvwmTaskBar: BellVolume 20
*FvwmTaskBar: AutoStick
*FvwmTaskBar: NoIconAction SendToModule FvwmAnimate animate
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click3 Menu FvwmWindowOpsMenu
*FvwmTaskBar: StartIcon mini/fvwm.png
*FvwmTaskBar: StartName Start
*FvwmTaskBar: StartMenu StartMenu
*FvwmTaskBar: StartIcon mini-exp.xpm
